</P>
<P>
BEIRUT -- The United Nations Secretary-General Kofi Annan
arrived here Friday morning on a two-day visit to Lebanon in the
third leg of his maiden tour to the region since he took office in
January 1997. (Annan-Lebanon-Arrival)
</P>
<P>
