<HEADLINE> More Visitors Watch China's Tibetan Art Exhibition  in Nepal </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, March 20 (Xinhua) -- As many as 3,000 local and
foreign people have visited the on-going China's Tibetan Art
Exhibition held at the Birendra International Convention Center
here, according to an official from the Chinese Embassy in Nepal
that sponsored it.
</P>
