<HEADLINE> Local Authorities in Tanzania Mismanage Funds </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, March 20 (Xinhua) -- More than half of the
local authorities in Tanzania have been accused of mismanaging
funds, media reports said Friday.
</P>
<P>
Of 103 councils of the country, 64 mismanaged about 3.5
billion shillings (about 5.8 million US dollars) between 1993 and
1996, the Controller and Auditor General has revealed.
