This is the first sitting American President to visit Uganda.
</P>
<P>
Mbabazi briefed the press that for the first day Clinton is to
hold talks with Ugandan President Yoweri Museveni on bilateral
relations and then to visit a school and a US-funded program
outside Kampala.
</P>
<P>
