Museveni on March 25 in Entebbe, some 40 kilometers south from
here. The summit will focus on regional issues including conflict
prevention, democratic participation, human rights promotion and
economic integration.
</P>
<P>
Mbabazi confirmed that leaders from Kenya, Tanzania, Rwanda,
the Democratic Republic of Congo and Zimbabwe, and the
Secretary-General of the Organization of African Unity are to
attend the summit.
</P>
<P>
