<HEADLINE> Shanghai Hosts Stamp Auction </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, March 21 (Xinhua) -- The Shanghai International
Commodity Auction Company recently was the host of a large auction
of Chinese stamps in which connoisseurs traded 395 items.
</P>
<P>
