as part of a government plan to provide jobs for 3,000 doctors,
the minister was quoted as saying at the opening session of the
conference.
</P>
<P>
The government has given top most priority to the education and
health sectors as it believed in the development of human
resources for attaining the target of self-reliance and
improvement, he stated.
</P>
<P>
The minister appreciated the dedicated and sincere efforts of
the NEDSB in initiating and bringing about a momentum in the
posthumous eye donation movement in the society. 
